abstract: The couple met in April at the Summit, a Tulsa social club, where they bonded over the songs of the Bee Gees.
snippet: The couple met in April at the Summit, a Tulsa social club, where they bonded over the songs of the Bee Gees.
lead_paragraph: Deborah Anne Gist and Ronnie Dale Jobe are to be married Dec. 22 at their home in Tulsa, Okla. The Rev. Courtney Richards, a Disciples of Christ minister, is to officiate, with the Rev. Mark R. Wood, an Episcopal priest, to take part.

abstract: Duncan Keith called out his club for its energy level after Wednesday's home loss to Colorado, but the Blackhawks veteran had nothing but praise for his teammates after Chicago rallied to pull out an improbable win against the Avalanche.
snippet: Duncan Keith called out his club for its energy level after Wednesday's home loss to Colorado, but the Blackhawks veteran had nothing but praise for his teammates after Chicago rallied to pull out an improbable win against the Avalanche.
lead_paragraph: DENVER — Duncan Keith called out his club for its energy level after Wednesday's home loss to Colorado, but the Blackhawks veteran had nothing but praise for his teammates after Chicago rallied to pull out an improbable win against the Avalanche.
headline_main: Blackhawks Score 4 in 3rd Period to Beat Avalanche 5-3

abstract: For years, members of a secret team, Unit 29155, operated without Western security officials having any idea about their activities. But an attack on an arms dealer in Sofia helped blow their cover.
snippet: For years, members of a secret team, Unit 29155, operated without Western security officials having any idea about their activities. But an attack on an arms dealer in Sofia helped blow their cover.
lead_paragraph: SOFIA, Bulgaria — The Russian assassin used an alias, Sergei Fedotov, and slipped into Bulgaria unnoticed, checking into a hotel in Sofia near the office of a local arms manufacturer who had been selling ammunition to Ukraine.

lead_paragraph: ST.-MALO, France — On a recent morning, toddlers and teenagers laughed and shouted as they skated around a rink of shiny ice just outside the walls of St.-Malo, a city on the northern coast of Brittany where winters generally hover above freezing.

headline_main: In France, Holiday Skating Rinks Are an Unlikely Climate Battleground
headline_print_headline: The Joys of Icy Strides,  Tempered by Concerns  Over Carbon Footprints

abstract: Since 2001, 23 public and private pools have appeared in Kabul, but only two allow women. They’re a welcome refuge from suicide bombings and the threat of a Taliban takeover.
snippet: Since 2001, 23 public and private pools have appeared in Kabul, but only two allow women. They’re a welcome refuge from suicide bombings and the threat of a Taliban takeover.
lead_paragraph: KABUL, Afghanistan — When Fatema Saeedi is in the pool, she cannot hear the crowded, chaotic noise of the city around her. She does not think about suicide bombings or Taliban attacks. She concentrates on her breathing as she moves through the water. One hand in front of the other. Exhale.

abstract: The new ride to orbit built for NASA and its astronauts returned to Earth after problems during its first trip to space on Friday.
snippet: The new ride to orbit built for NASA and its astronauts returned to Earth after problems during its first trip to space on Friday.
lead_paragraph: Boeing’s new spacecraft, the CST-100 Starliner, safely parachuted to Earth on Sunday, landing atop inflated airbags before dawn at the White Sands Missile Range in New Mexico.

abstract: The couple met in 2004 at a friend’s birthday party in Park Slope, Brooklyn.
snippet: The couple met in 2004 at a friend’s birthday party in Park Slope, Brooklyn.
lead_paragraph: Meredith Reade Miller and Kimberly Ann Duva were married Dec. 16 at their apartment in Manhattan. Hilary Gingold, a civil court judge with chambers in Brooklyn, officiated.

abstract: The couple met at Princeton, from which each graduated, the bride cum laude and the groom summa cum laude.
snippet: The couple met at Princeton, from which each graduated, the bride cum laude and the groom summa cum laude.
lead_paragraph: Diane Shuyan Hu and Alexander Joseph William Sappington were married Dec. 20 at Villa Serenita, a rental home in St. Thomas, in the United States Virgin Islands. Michael Motylinski, who received an online ordination through the Wanderlust Bay Ministries, officiated.

abstract: Joe Dolincheck threw six touchdown passes, Arnijae Ponder had 30 carries for 130 yards, and Morningside beat Marian 40-38 on Saturday night to claim its second consecutive NAIA national championship.
snippet: Joe Dolincheck threw six touchdown passes, Arnijae Ponder had 30 carries for 130 yards, and Morningside beat Marian 40-38 on Saturday night to claim its second consecutive NAIA national championship.
lead_paragraph: GRAMBLING, La. — Joe Dolincheck threw six touchdown passes, Arnijae Ponder had 30 carries for 130 yards, and Morningside beat Marian 40-38 on Saturday night to claim its second consecutive NAIA national championship.
headline_main: Morningside Beats Marian, Wins Second Straight NAIA Title
headline_print_headline: Morningside Beats Marian, Wins Second Straight NAIA Title

abstract: Gavin Kensmil scored 21 points, Cameron Johnson added 18 and Stephen F. Austin held off McNeese for an 81-73 win on Saturday night.
snippet: Gavin Kensmil scored 21 points, Cameron Johnson added 18 and Stephen F. Austin held off McNeese for an 81-73 win on Saturday night.
lead_paragraph: LAKE CHARLES, La. — Gavin Kensmil scored 21 points, Cameron Johnson added 18 and Stephen F. Austin held off McNeese for an 81-73 win on Saturday night.
headline_main: Stephen F. Austin Holds Off McNeese 81-73
headline_print_headline: Stephen F. Austin Holds Off McNeese 81-73
